00:06:01.260 --> 00:06:03.260
(Risadas)

00:06:03.260 --> 00:06:05.260
Oops.

00:06:05.260 --> 00:06:08.260
(Risadas)

00:06:08.260 --> 00:06:10.260
Aqui está outra realmente ruim.

00:06:10.260 --> 00:06:12.260
JohnEdwards.com

00:06:12.260 --> 00:06:15.260
(Texto: Maldito liberal)

00:06:15.260 --> 00:06:17.260
(Risadas)

00:06:17.260 --> 00:06:20.260
